{
  "page": "Jeyne Beesbury",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Beesbury\" title=\"House Beesbury\"><img alt=\"House Beesbury.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/House_Beesbury.svg/50px-House_Beesbury.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/House_Beesbury.svg/75px-House_Beesbury.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/House_Beesbury.svg/100px-House_Beesbury.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jeyne Beesbury</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Beesbury\" title=\"House Beesbury\">House Beesbury</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nlate <a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a> or early <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Frey\" title=\"Rhaegar Frey\">Rhaegar Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Frey_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Robert Frey (son of Rhaegar)\">Robert Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Rhaegar)\">Walda Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Frey\" title=\"Jonos Frey\">Jonos Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jeyne Beesbury</b> is a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Beesbury\" title=\"House Beesbury\">House Beesbury</a> and the wife of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Frey\" title=\"Rhaegar Frey\">Rhaegar Frey</a>, with whom she has three children, <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Frey_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Robert Frey (son of Rhaegar)\">Robert</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Rhaegar)\">Walda</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Frey\" title=\"Jonos Frey\">Jonos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Beesbury&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Beesbury&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Jeyne dies of a wasting <a href=\"/index.php/Illness\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Illness\">illness</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Beesbury&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Jeyne's widower, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Frey\" title=\"Rhaegar Frey\">Rhaegar Frey</a>, is betrothed to <a href=\"/index.php/Wynafryd_Manderly\" title=\"Wynafryd Manderly\">Wynafryd Manderly</a>, granddaughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_White_Harbor\" title=\"Lord of White Harbor\">Lord of White Harbor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Rhaegar mysteriously disappears on his way to <a href=\"/index.php/Barrowton\" title=\"Barrowton\">Barrowton</a> and is presumed dead, however. Thus making Jeyne's three children orphans.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Beesbury&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jeyne's relation to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Warryn_Beesbury\" title=\"Warryn Beesbury\">Warryn Beesbury</a>, the head of the House, is unknown. \n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width: